@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="mb-4 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-muted text-center">Last updated: June 2025</p>

        <p>
            MBS Software Limited is committed to protecting your privacy. This statement outlines how ePegboard handles data within the application and on our website.
        </p>

        <h3 class="mt-5">🔧 Application Privacy (ePegboard Software)</h3>

        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>No personal player data is collected or transmitted automatically.</strong><br />
                ePegboard does not send any personally identifiable player information (e.g. names, emails, contact details) to MBS Software or any third parties.
            </li>

            <li>
                <strong>Admin-controlled data only.</strong><br />
                Club organisers may choose to enter player names or contact details. This data is stored locally and is never accessed by MBS Software.
            </li>

            <li>
                <strong>Club-identified usage statistics.</strong><br />
                The application may occasionally send usage data that identifies the club (such as session counts or attendance). This information is used solely to monitor licensing and improve product features. No player-level data is included.
            </li>

            <li>
                <strong>Offline functionality.</strong><br />
                ePegboard operates fully offline during sessions. An internet connection is only required to activate licensing and optionally share usage stats.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mt-5">🌐 Website Privacy</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Cookies and analytics.</strong><br />
                The ePegboard website may use basic cookies or analytics tools (such as Google Analytics) to monitor usage. No personal information is collected unless explicitly submitted by the user.
            </li>

            <li>
                <strong>Contact forms and email.</strong><br />
                If you contact us, your information is used solely for that communication. We do not share or sell your data.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mt-5">🔒 Your Rights</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>You may request a copy of any personal data we've received.</li>
            <li>You may request deletion of your data at any time.</li>
            <li>To make a request, email us at <a href="mailto:admin@epegboard.com">admin@epegboard.com</a>.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mt-5">📍 Data Storage</h3>
        <p>
            All data entered into the ePegboard software is stored locally on your club’s own computer or device. MBS Software does not host or have access to your session or member data.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
